# Async Runtime Module
#
# Core async/await runtime for Simple language.
# Provides futures, tasks, executors, and async I/O primitives.
#
# Features:
#   - Future-based async execution
#   - Task spawning and scheduling
#   - Async I/O operations
#   - Promise/future combinators
#   - Multi-executor support
#
# Public API:
#   - use std.async.future.{Future, async_fn}
#   - use std.async.task.{Task, spawn_task}
#   - use std.async.runtime.{AsyncRuntime, run_async}
#   - use std.async.executor.{Executor}
#   - use std.async.promise.{Promise, PromiseResolver}
#
# Components:
#   - Future: Core async abstraction
#   - Task: Unit of async work
#   - Executor: Task scheduler
#   - Runtime: Complete async environment
#   - Poll: Polling mechanism
#   - Combinators: Future composition (map, then, join)
#   - I/O: Async file/network operations
#   - FFI: Native async integration

# All submodules are automatically available through the module system.
